Interface Client.ClientManager

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Driver
    Enclosing class:
    Client

    public static interface Client.ClientManager
    Communicate the Client's state to a driver program. Pass an instance of this to the constructor if you want the client to update you regarding state changes. The implementor is responsible for ensuring thread safety.
